GB2312;\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">主席：尚福林<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"layout-grid-mode:char;line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:10pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n<\/span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/span><\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">二<\/span><span><span style=\"color:black;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">○<\/span><\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">一二年六月七日<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span>&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><span style=\"font-family:黑体;font-size:18pt;\">商业银行资本管理办法（试行）<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><span style=\"font-family:黑体;\">第一章<span><span>&nbsp;\r\n<\/span><\/span>总则<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span>&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第一条<span><span> <\/span><\/span><\/span><\/b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>&nbsp; <\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">为加强商业银行资本监管，维护银行体系稳健运行，保护存款人利益，根据《中华人民共和国银行业监督管理法》、《中华人民共和国商业银行法》、《中华人民共和国外资银行管理条例》等法律法规，制定本办法。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第二条<span><span> <\/span><\/span><\/span><\/b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp; <\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">本办法适用于在中华人民共和国境内设立的商业银行。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第三条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>\r\n<\/span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp; <\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行资本应抵御其所面临的风险，包括个体风险和系统性风险。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第四条<span><span> <\/span><\/span><\/span><\/b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp; <\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行应当符合本办法规定的资本充足率监管要求。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第五条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>\r\n<\/span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp; <\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">本办法所称资本充足率，是指商业银行持有的符合本办法规定的资本与风险加权资产之间的比率。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">一级资本充足率，是指商业银行持有的符合本办法规定的一级资本与风险加权资产之间的比率。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">核心一级资本充足率，是指商业银行持有的符合本办法规定的核心一级资本与风险加权资产之间的比率。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第六条<span><span> <\/span><\/span><\/span><\/b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp; <\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行应当按照本办法的规定计算并表和未并表的资本充足率。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第七条<span><span> <\/span><\/span><\/span><\/b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp; <\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行资本充足率计算应当建立在充分计<span>提贷<\/span>款损失准备等各项减值准备的基础之上。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第八条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>\r\n<\/span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp; <\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行应当按照本办法建立全面风险管理架构和内部资本充足评估程序。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第九条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>\r\n<\/span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp; <\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">中国银行业监督管理委员会（以下简称银监会）依照本办法对商业银行资本充足率、资本管理状况进行监督检查，并采取相应的监管措施。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第十条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>\r\n<\/span><span>&nbsp; <\/span><span>&nbsp;<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行应当按照本办法披露资本充足率信息。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p><!---doc_text---><div align=\"right\"><table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\r\n<tr><td class=\"doc_sign\" align=\"center\"><img data-baiduimageplus-ignore src=\"http://icons.xici.net/u16386958/files/sign.pic\"><\/td><\/tr>\r\n<tr><td class=\"doc_sign\" align=\"center\">\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\"><tr><td class=\"doc_sign\">我的名片：<br>\r\n创建紫金家园，打造职场互动沟通平台；<br>\r\n关注基层民声，创造健康和谐企业氛围；<br>\r\n南京拍客（摄影）：我是南京人，传播真善美！&nbsp;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n本版腾讯微博：http://t.qq.com/zijibank<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;新浪微博：http://weibo.com/jszjrcbank<br>\r\n<\/td><\/tr><\/table>\r\n<\/td><\/tr>\r\n<tr><td class=\"doc_sign\" align=\"center\"><a href=\"http://b1123492.xici.net\" target=\"_blank\">紫金家园<\/a><\/td><\/tr>\r\n<\/table><\/div><\/div>\r\n","isAdminFlag":false,"isCanUpdate":false,"isDel":0,"isHide":0,"isShow":true,"keyThis":"","lDocModifiedCount":1,"LongDate":"12-07-01 22:35","online":false,"really_updated_at":"2012-07-01 22:35:22","ShortDate":"07-01 22:35","ShortDate_i":[],"Url":"/d172277779.u16386958.htm","UserID":16386958,"UserName":"富民强企","UseVote":false,"v_isAdminDeleted":false,"v_isAppend":false,"v_isEditOwnDoc":false,"v_lDocModifiedPageNo":0,"v_lDocNo":0,"v_lPageCount":1.00000000000000000e+000,"v_lUserID":0,"v_lUserLevel":100,"v_SeeUserId":0},"isfirstfloor":true,"similar_thread":[]},{"docinfo":{},"foolrinfo":{"del_w":false,"DelTime":"","Emote":0,"fd_1_sel_product":false,"fd_id":0,"floorcontent":"<div class=doc_txt  id=\"text_2_0\"><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><span style=\"font-family:黑体;\">第二章<span><span>&nbsp;\r\n<\/span><\/span>资本充足率计算和监管要求<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span>&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><b><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;\">第一节\r\n资本充足率计算范围<span><\/span><\/span><\/b><\/p>\r\n<p><span>&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第十一条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>&nbsp;\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行未并<span>表资本<\/span>充足率的计算范围应包括商业银行境内外所有分支机构。并<span>表资本<\/span>充足率的计算范围应包括商业银行以及符合本办法规定的其直接或间接投资的金融机构。商业银行及被投资金融机构共同构成银行集团。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第十二条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>&nbsp;\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行计算并<span>表资本<\/span>充足率，应当将以下境内外被投资金融机构纳入并表范围：<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（一）商业银行直接或间接拥有<span>50%<\/span>以上表决权的被投资金融机构。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（二）商业银行拥有<span>50%<\/span>以下（含）表决权的被投资金融机构，但与被投资金融机构之间有下列情况之一的，应将其纳入并表范围：<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">1<\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">．通过与其它投资者之间的协议，拥有该金融机构<span>50%<\/span>以上的表决权。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">2<\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">．根据章程或协议，有权决定该金融机构的财务和经营政策。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">3<\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">．有权任免该金融机构董事会或类似权力机构的多数成员。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">4<\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">．在被投资金融机构董事会或类似权力机构占多数表决权。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">确定对被投资金融机构表决权时，应考虑直接和间接拥有的被投资金融机构的当期可转换债券、当期可执行的认股权证等潜在表决权因素，对于当期可以实现的潜在表决权，应计入对被投资金融机构的表决权。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（三）其它证据表明商业银行实际控制被投资金融机构的情况。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">控制，是指一个公司能够决定另一个公司的财务和经营政策，并据以从另一个公司的经营活动中获取利益。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第十三条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>&nbsp;\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行未拥有被投资金融机构多数表决权或控制权，具有下列情况之一的，应当纳入并<span>表资本<\/span>充足率计算范围：<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（一）具有业务同质性的多个金融机构，虽然单个金融机构资产规模占银行集团整体资产规模的比例较小，但该类金融机构总体风险足以对银行集团的财务状况及风险水平造成重大影响。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（二）被投资金融机构所产生的合<span>规<\/span>风险、声誉风险造成的危害和损失足以对银行集团的声誉造成重大影响。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第十四条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>&nbsp;\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">符合本办法第十二条、第十三条规定的保险公司不纳入并表范围。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行<span>应从各级<\/span>资本中对应扣除对保险公司的资本投资，若保险公司存在资本缺口的，还应当扣除相应的资本缺口。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第十五条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>&nbsp;\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行拥有被投资金融机构<span>50<\/span>％以上表决权或对被投资金融机构的控制权，但被投资金融机构处于以下状态之一的，可不列入并表范围：<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（一）已关闭或已宣布破产。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（二）因终止而进入清算程序。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（三）受所在国外汇管制及其它突发事件的影响，资金调度受到限制的境外被投资金融机构。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行对有前款规定情形的被投资金融机构资本投资的处理方法按照本办法第十四条第二款的规定执行。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第十六条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>&nbsp;\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行计算未并<span>表资本<\/span>充足率，应当从各级资本中对应扣除其对符合本办法第十二条和第十三条规定的金融机构的所有资本投资。若这些金融机构存在资本缺口的，还应当扣除相应的资本缺口。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第十七条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>&nbsp;\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行应当根据本办法制定并表和未并<span>表资本<\/span>充足率计算内部制度。商业银行调整并表和未并<span>表资本<\/span>充足率计算范围的，应说明理由，并及时报银监会备案。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第十八条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>&nbsp;\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">银监会有权根据商业银行及其附属机构股权结构变动、业务类别及风险状况确定和调整其并<span>表资本<\/span>充足率的计算范围。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span>&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><b><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;\">第二节\r\n资本充足率计算公式<span><\/span><\/span><\/b><\/p>\r\n<p><span>&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第十九条<\/span><\/b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>&nbsp; <\/span><span>&nbsp; <\/span><\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行应当按照以下公式计算资本充足率：<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:36pt;text-align:left;text-indent:23.55pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>&nbsp;<\/span><sub> <\/sub><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:36pt;text-align:left;text-indent:23.55pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><sub><\/sub><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><sub><\/sub><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第二十条<\/span><\/b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>&nbsp; <\/span><span>&nbsp; <\/span><\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行总资本包括核心一级资本、其它一级资本和二级资本。商业银行应当按照本办法第三章的规定计算各级资本和扣除项。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第二十一条<\/span><\/b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>&nbsp; <\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行风险加权资产包括信用风险加权资产、市场风险加权资产和操作风险加权资产。商业银行应当按照本办法第四章、第五章和第六章的规定分别计量信用风险加权资产、市场风险加权资产和操作风险加权资产。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:30pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><b><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;\">第三节\r\n资本充足率监管要求<span><\/span><\/span><\/b><\/p>\r\n<p><span>&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第二十二条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>&nbsp;\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行资本充足率监管要求包括最低资本要求、储备资本和<span>逆周期<\/span>资本要求、系统重要性银行附加资本要求以及第二支柱资本要求。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第二十三条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>&nbsp;\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行各级资本充足率不得低于如下最低要求：<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（一）核心一级资本充足率不得低于<span>5%<\/span>。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（二）一级资本充足率不得低于<span>6%<\/span>。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（三）资本充足率不得低于<span>8%<\/span>。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第二十四条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>&nbsp;\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行应当在最低资本要求的基础上计提储备资本。储备资本要求为风险加权资产的<span>2.5%<\/span>，由核心一级资本来满足。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">特定情况下，商业银行应当在最低资本要求和储备资本要求之上计提逆周期资本。逆周期资本要求为风险加权资产的<span>0-2.5%<\/span>，由核心一级资本来满足。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">逆周期资本的计提与运用规则另行规定。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第二十五条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>&nbsp;\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">除本办法第二十三条和第二十四条规定的最低资本要求、储备资本和<span>逆周期<\/span>资本要求外，系统重要性银行还应当计提附加资本。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">国内系统重要性银行附加资本要求为风险加权资产的<span>1%<\/span>，由核心一级资本满足。国内系统重要性银行的认定标准另行规定。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">若国内银行被认定为全球系统重要性银行，所适用的附加资本要求不得低于巴塞尔委员会的统一规定。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第二十六条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>&nbsp;\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">除本办法第二十三条、第二十四条和第二十五条规定的资本要求以外，银监会有权在第二支柱框架下提出更审慎的资本要求，确保资本充分覆盖风险，包括：<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（一）根据风险判断，针对部分资产组合提出的特定资本要求；<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（二）根据监督检查结果，针对单家银行提出的特定资本要求。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第二十七条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>&nbsp;\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">除上述资本充足率监管要求外，商业银行还应当满足杠杆率监管要求。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">杠杆率的计算规则和监管要求另行规定。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span>&nbsp;<\/span><\/p><div align=\"right\"><table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\r\n<tr><td class=\"doc_sign\" align=\"center\"><img data-baiduimageplus-ignore src=\"http://icons.xici.net/u16386958/files/sign.pic\"><\/td><\/tr>\r\n<tr><td class=\"doc_sign\" align=\"center\">\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\"><tr><td class=\"doc_sign\">我的名片：<br>\r\n创建紫金家园，打造职场互动沟通平台；<br>\r\n关注基层民声，创造健康和谐企业氛围；<br>\r\n南京拍客（摄影）：我是南京人，传播真善美！&nbsp;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n本版腾讯微博：http://t.qq.com/zijibank<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;新浪微博：http://weibo.com/jszjrcbank<br>\r\n<\/td><\/tr><\/table>\r\n<\/td><\/tr>\r\n<tr><td class=\"doc_sign\" align=\"center\"><a href=\"http://b1123492.xici.net\" target=\"_blank\">紫金家园<\/a><\/td><\/tr>\r\n<\/table><\/div><\/div>\r\n","isAdminFlag":false,"isCanUpdate":false,"isDel":0,"isHide":0,"isShow":true,"keyThis":"","lDocModifiedCount":1,"LongDate":"12-07-01 22:36","online":false,"really_updated_at":"2012-07-01 22:36:38","ShortDate":"07-01 22:36","ShortDate_i":[],"Url":"/d172277779.u16386958.htm","UserID":16386958,"UserName":"富民强企","UseVote":false,"v_isAdminDeleted":false,"v_isAppend":false,"v_isEditOwnDoc":false,"v_lDocModifiedPageNo":0,"v_lDocNo":1,"v_lPageCount":1.00000000000000000e+000,"v_lUserID":0,"v_lUserLevel":100,"v_SeeUserId":0},"isfirstfloor":false},{"docinfo":{},"foolrinfo":{"del_w":false,"DelTime":"","Emote":0,"fd_1_sel_product":false,"fd_id":0,"floorcontent":"<div class=doc_txt  id=\"text_3_0\"><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><span style=\"font-family:黑体;\">第三章<span><span>&nbsp;\r\n<\/span><\/span>资本定义<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span>&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><b><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;\">第一节\r\n资本组成<span><\/span><\/span><\/b><\/p>\r\n<p><span>&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第二十八条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>&nbsp;\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行发行的资本工具应符合本办法附件<span>1<\/span>规定的合格标准。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第二十九条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>&nbsp;\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">核心一级资本包括：<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（一）<span><span> <\/span><\/span>实收资本或普通股。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（二）<span><span> <\/span><\/span>资本公积。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（三）<span><span> <\/span><\/span>盈余公积。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（四）<span><span> <\/span><\/span>一般风险准备。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（五）<span><span> <\/span><\/span>未分配利润。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（六）少数股东资本可计入部分。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第三十条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>&nbsp;\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">其它一级资本包括：<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（一）<span><span> <\/span><\/span>其它一级资本工具及其溢价。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（二）<span><span> <\/span><\/span>少数股东资本可计入部分。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第三十一条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>&nbsp;\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">二级资本包括：<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（一）<span><span> <\/span><\/span>二级资本工具及其溢价。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（二）<span><span> <\/span><\/span>超额贷款损失准备。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">1.<\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行采用权重法计量信用风险加权资产的，超额贷款损失准备可计入二级资本，但不得超过信用风险加权资产的<span>1.25%<\/span>。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">前款所称超额贷款损失准备是指商业银行<span>实际计提<\/span>的贷款损失准备超过最低要求的部分。贷款损失准备最低要求指<span>100%<\/span>拨备覆盖率对应的贷款损失准备和应计提的贷款损失专项准备两者中的较大者。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">2.<\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行采用内部评级法计量信用风险加权资产的，超额贷款损失准备可计入二级资本，但不得超过信用风险加权资产的<span>0.6%<\/span>。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">前款所称超额贷款损失准备是指商业银行<span>实际计提<\/span>的贷款损失准备超过预期损失的部分。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（三）<span><span> <\/span><\/span>少数股东资本可计入部分。<span>\r\n<\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:center;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;\">第二节 资本扣除项<span><\/span><\/span><\/b><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第三十二条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>&nbsp;\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">计算资本充足率时，商业银行应当从核心一级资本中全额扣除以下项目：<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（一）<span><span> <\/span><\/span>商誉。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（二）<span><span> <\/span><\/span>其它无形资产（土地使用权除外）。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（三）<span><span> <\/span><\/span>由经营亏损引起的<span>净递延税<\/span>资产。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（四）<span><span> <\/span><\/span>贷款损失准备缺口。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">1.<\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行采用权重法计量信用风险加权资产的，贷款损失准备缺口是指商业银行<span>实际计提<\/span>的贷款损失准备低于贷款损失准备最低要求的部分。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">2.<\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行采用内部评级法计量信用风险加权资产的，贷款损失准备缺口是指商业银行<span>实际计提<\/span>的贷款损失准备低于预期损失的部分。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（五）<span><span> <\/span><\/span>资产证券化销售利得。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（六）<span><span> <\/span><\/span>确定受益类的养老金资产净额。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（七）<span><span> <\/span><\/span>直接或间接持有本银行的股票。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（八）<span><span> <\/span><\/span>对资产负债表中未按公允价值计量的项目进行套期形成的现金流储备，若为正值，应予以扣除；若为负值，应予以加回。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（九）<span><span> <\/span><\/span>商业银行自身信用风险变化导致其负债公允价值变化带来的未实现损益。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第三十三条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>&nbsp;\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行之间通过协议相互持有的各级资本工具，或银监会认定为虚增资本的各级资本投资，应从相应监管资本中对应扣除。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行直接或间接持有本银行发行的其他一级资本工具和二级资本工具，应从相应的监管资本中对应扣除。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">对应扣除是指从商业银行自身相应层级资本中扣除。商业银行某一级资本净额小于应扣除数额的，缺口部分应从更高一级的资本净额中扣除。<span>\r\n<\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第三十四条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>&nbsp;\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行对未并<span>表金融<\/span>机构的小额少数资本投资，合计超出本银行核心一级资本净额<span>10%<\/span>的部分，<span>应从各级<\/span>监管资本中对应扣除。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">小额少数资本投资是指商业银行对金融机构各级资本投资（包括直接和间接投资）占该被投资金融机构实收资本（普通股加普通股溢价）<span>10<\/span>％（不含）以下，且不符合本办法第十二条、第十三条规定的资本投资。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第三十五条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>&nbsp;\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行对未并<span>表金融<\/span>机构的大额少数资本投资中，核心一级资本投资合计超出本行核心一级资本净额<span>10%<\/span>的部分应从本银行核心一级资本中扣除；其它一级资本投资和二级资本投资应从相应层级资本中全额扣除。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">大额少数资本投资是指商业银行对金融机构各级资本投资（包括直接和间接投资）占该被投资金融机构实收资本（普通股加普通股溢价）<span>10<\/span>％（含）以上，且不符合本办法第十二条、第十三条规定的资本投资。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第三十六条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>&nbsp;\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">除本办法第三十二条第三款规定的递<span>延税资产<\/span>外，其它依赖于本银行未来盈利的<span>净递延税<\/span>资产，超出本行核心一级资本净额<span>10%<\/span>的部分应从核心一级资本中扣除。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第三十七条<span><span>&nbsp; <\/span><\/span><\/span><\/b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">根据本办法第三十五条、第三十六条的规定，未在商业银行核心一级资本中扣除的对金融机构的大额少数资本投资和相应的<span>净递延税<\/span>资产，合计金额不得超过本行核心一级资本净额的<span>15%<\/span>。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><b><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/b><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><b><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;\">第三节\r\n少数股东资本的处理<span><\/span><\/span><\/b><\/p>\r\n<p><span>&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第三十八条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>&nbsp;\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行附属公司适用于资本充足率监管的，附属公司直接发行且由第三方持有的少数股东资本可以部分计入监管资本。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第三十九条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>&nbsp;\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">附属公司核心一级资本中少数股东资本用于满足核心一级资本最低要求和储备资本要求的部分，可计入并<span>表核心<\/span>一级资本。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">最低要求和储备资本要求为下面两项中较小者：<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（一）附属公司核心一级资本最低要求加储备资本要求。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（二）母公司并<span>表核心<\/span>一级资本最低要求与储备资本要求归属于附属公司的部分。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第四十条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>&nbsp;\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">附属公司一级资本中少数股东资本用于满足一级资本最低要求和储备资本要求的部分，扣除已计入并<span>表核心<\/span>一级资本的部分后，剩余部分可以计入并表其它一级资本。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">最低要求和储备资本要求为下面两项中较小者：<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（一）附属公司一级资本最低要求加储备资本要求。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（二）母公司并表一级资本最低要求与储备资本要求归属于附属公司的部分。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第四十一条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>&nbsp;\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">附属公司总资本中少数股东资本用于满足总资本最低要求和储备资本要求的部分，扣除已计入并表一级资本的部分后，剩余部分可以计入并表二级资本。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">最低要求和储备资本要求为下面两项中较小者：<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（一）附属公司总资本最低要求加储备资本要求。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（二）母公司<span>并表总资本<\/span>最低要求与储备资本要求归属于附属公司的部分。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span>&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><b><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;\">第四节\r\n特殊规定<span><\/span><\/span><\/b><\/p>\r\n<p><span>&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第四十二条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>&nbsp;\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行发行的二级资本工具有确定到期日的，该二级资本工具在距到期日前最后五年，可计入二级资本的金额，应当按<span>100%<\/span>、<span>80%<\/span>、<span>60%<\/span>、<span>40%<\/span>、<span>20%<\/span>的比例逐年减计。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第四十三条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>&nbsp;\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行<span>2010<\/span>年<span>9<\/span>月<span>12<\/span>日前发行的不合格二级资本工具，<span>2013<\/span>年<span>1<\/span>月<span>1<\/span>日之前可计入监管资本，<span>2013<\/span>年<span>1<\/span>月<span>1<\/span>日起按年递减<span>10%<\/span>，<span>2022<\/span>年<span>1<\/span>月<span>1<\/span>日起<span>不<\/span>得计入监管资本。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">前款所称不合格二级资本工具按年递减数量的计算以<span>2013<\/span>年<span>1<\/span>月<span>1<\/span>日的数量为基数。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">带有利率跳升机制或其它赎回激励的二级资本工具，<span>若行<\/span>权日期在<span>2013<\/span>年<span>1<\/span>月<span>1<\/span>日之后，且在行权日未被赎回，并满足本办法附件<span>1<\/span>规定的其它所有合格标准，可继续计入监管资本。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第四十四条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>&nbsp;\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行<span>2010<\/span>年<span>9<\/span>月<span>12<\/span>日至<span>2013<\/span>年<span>1<\/span>月<span>1<\/span>日之间发行的二级资本工具，若<span>不含有减记或<\/span>转股条款，但满足本办法附件<span>1<\/span>规定的其它合格标准，<span>2013<\/span>年<span>1<\/span>月<span>1<\/span>日之前可计入监管资本，<span>2013<\/span>年<span>1<\/span>月<span>1<\/span>日起按年递减<span>10%<\/span>，<span>2022<\/span>年<span>1<\/span>月<span>1<\/span>日起<span>不<\/span>得计入监管资本。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">前款所称不合格二级资本工具按年递减数量的计算以<span>2013<\/span>年<span>1<\/span>月<span>1<\/span>日的数量为基数。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第四十五条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>&nbsp;\r\n<\/span>2013<span><span>年1<\/span><\/span><span><span>月1<\/span><\/span><span><span>日<\/span><\/span><span>之后发行的不合格资本工具不再计入监管资本。<\/span><\/span><\/p><div align=\"right\"><table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\r\n<tr><td class=\"doc_sign\" align=\"center\"><img data-baiduimageplus-ignore src=\"http://icons.xici.net/u16386958/files/sign.pic\"><\/td><\/tr>\r\n<tr><td class=\"doc_sign\" align=\"center\">\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\"><tr><td class=\"doc_sign\">我的名片：<br>\r\n创建紫金家园，打造职场互动沟通平台；<br>\r\n关注基层民声，创造健康和谐企业氛围；<br>\r\n南京拍客（摄影）：我是南京人，传播真善美！&nbsp;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n本版腾讯微博：http://t.qq.com/zijibank<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;新浪微博：http://weibo.com/jszjrcbank<br>\r\n<\/td><\/tr><\/table>\r\n<\/td><\/tr>\r\n<tr><td class=\"doc_sign\" align=\"center\"><a href=\"http://b1123492.xici.net\" target=\"_blank\">紫金家园<\/a><\/td><\/tr>\r\n<\/table><\/div><\/div>\r\n","isAdminFlag":false,"isCanUpdate":false,"isDel":0,"isHide":0,"isShow":true,"keyThis":"","lDocModifiedCount":1,"LongDate":"12-07-01 22:37","online":false,"really_updated_at":"2012-07-01 22:37:19","ShortDate":"07-01 22:37","ShortDate_i":[],"Url":"/d172277779.u16386958.htm","UserID":16386958,"UserName":"富民强企","UseVote":false,"v_isAdminDeleted":false,"v_isAppend":false,"v_isEditOwnDoc":false,"v_lDocModifiedPageNo":0,"v_lDocNo":2,"v_lPageCount":1.00000000000000000e+000,"v_lUserID":0,"v_lUserLevel":100,"v_SeeUserId":0},"isfirstfloor":false},{"docinfo":{},"foolrinfo":{"del_w":false,"DelTime":"","Emote":0,"fd_1_sel_product":false,"fd_id":0,"floorcontent":"<div class=doc_txt  id=\"text_4_0\"><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><span style=\"font-family:黑体;\">第四章<span><span>&nbsp;\r\n<\/span><\/span>信用风险加权资产计量<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span>&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><b><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;\">第一节\r\n一般规定<span><\/span><\/span><\/b><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第四十六条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>&nbsp;\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行可以采用权重法或内部评级法计量信用风险加权资产。商业银行采用内部评级法计量信用风险加权资产的，应当符合本办法的规定，<span>并经银监<\/span>会核准。内部评级法未覆盖的风险暴露应采用权重法计量信用风险加权资产。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">未经银监会核准，商业银行不得变更信用风险加权资产计量方法。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第四十七条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>&nbsp;\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行申请采用内部评级法计量信用风险加权资产的，提交申请时内部评级<span>法资产<\/span>覆盖率应不低于<span>50%<\/span>，并在三年内达到<span>80%<\/span>。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">前款所称内部评级<span>法资产<\/span>覆盖率按以下公式确定：<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">内部评级<span>法资产<\/span>覆盖率<span>=<\/span>按内部评级法计量的风险加权资产<span>/<\/span>（按内部评级法计量的风险加权资产＋按权重法计量的内部评级法未覆盖信用风险暴露的风险加权资产）×<span>100%<\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第四十八条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>&nbsp;\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行采用内部评级法，应当按照本办法附件<span>3<\/span>的规定计量信用风险加权资产，按照本办法附件<span>4<\/span>的规定对银行账户信用风险暴露进行分类，按照本办法附件<span>5<\/span>的规定建立内部评级体系。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行采用内部评级法，可以按照本办法附件<span>6<\/span>的规定审慎考虑信用风险缓释工具的风险抵补作用。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行采用内部评级法，可以按照本办法附件<span>7<\/span>的规定采用监管映射法计量专业贷款信用风险加权资产。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第四十九条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>&nbsp;\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行应当按照本办法附件<span>8<\/span>的规定计量银行账户和交易账户的交易对手信用风险加权资产。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第五十条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>&nbsp;\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行应当按照本办法附件<span>9<\/span>的规定计量资产证券化风险暴露的信用风险加权资产。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span>&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><b><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;\">第二节\r\n权重法<span><\/span><\/span><\/b><\/p>\r\n<p><span>&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第五十一条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>&nbsp;\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">权重法下信用风险加权资产为银行账户表内资产信用风险加权资产与表外项目信用风险加权资产之<span>和<\/span>。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第五十二条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>&nbsp;\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行计量各类表内资产的风险加权资产，应首先从资产账面价值中扣除相应的减值准备，然后乘以风险权重。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第五十三条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>&nbsp;\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行计量各类表外项目的风险加权资产，应将表外项目名义金额乘以信用转换系数得到等值的表内资产，再按表内资产的处理方式计量风险加权资产。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第五十四条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>&nbsp;\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">现金及现金等价物的风险权重为<span>0<\/span>％。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第五十五条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>&nbsp;\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行对境外主权和金融机构债权的风险权重，以所在国家或地区的外部信用评级结果为基准。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（一）对其它国家或地区政府及其中央银行债权，该国家或地区的评级为<span>AA-<\/span>（含）以上的，风险权重为<span>0%<\/span>；<span>AA-<\/span>以下，<span>A-<\/span>（含）以上的，风险权重为<span>20%<\/span>；<span>A-<\/span>以下，<span>BBB-<\/span>（含）以上的，风险权重为<span>50%<\/span>；<span>BBB-<\/span>以下，<span>B-<\/span>（含）以上的，风险权重为<span>100%<\/span>；<span>B-<\/span>以下的，风险权重为<span>150%<\/span>；未评级的，风险权重为<span>100%<\/span>。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（二）对公共部门实体债权的风险权重与对所在国家或地区注册的商业银行债权的风险权重相同。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（三）对境外商业银行债权，注册地所在国家或地区的评级为<span>AA-<\/span>（含）以上的，风险权重为<span>25%<\/span>；<span>AA-<\/span>以下，<span>A-<\/span>（含）以上的，风险权重为<span>50%<\/span>；<span>A-<\/span>以下，<span>B-<\/span>（含）以上的，风险权重为<span>100%<\/span>；<span>B-<\/span>以下的，风险权重为<span>150%<\/span>；未评级的，风险权重为<span>100%<\/span>。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（四）对境外其它金融机构债权的风险权重为<span>100%<\/span>。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第五十六条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>&nbsp;\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行对多边开发银行、国际清算银行和国际货币基金组织债权的风险权重为<span>0%<\/span>。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">多边开发银行包括世界银行集团、亚洲开发银行、非洲开发银行、欧洲复兴开发银行、泛美开发银行、欧洲投资银行、欧洲投资基金、北欧投资银行、加勒比海开发银行、伊斯兰开发银行和欧洲开发银行理事会。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第五十七条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>&nbsp;\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行对我国中央政府和中国人民银行债权的风险权重为<span>0%<\/span>。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第五十八条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>&nbsp;\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行对我国公共部门实体债权的风险权重为<span>20%<\/span>。我国公共部门实体包括：<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（一）除财政部和中国人民银行以外，其它收入主要源于中央财政的公共部门。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（二）省级（直辖区、自治区）以及计划单列市人民政府。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行对前款所列公共部门实体投资的工商企业的债权不适用<span>20%<\/span>的风险权重。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第五十九条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>&nbsp;\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行对我国政策性银行债权的风险权重为<span>0%<\/span>。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行对我国政策性银行的次级债权（未扣除部分）的风险权重为<span>100%<\/span>。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第六十条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>&nbsp;\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行持有我国中央政府投资的金融资产管理公司为收购国有银行不良贷款而定向发行的债券的风险权重为<span>0%<\/span>。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行对我国中央政府投资的金融资产管理公司其它债权的风险权重为<span>100%<\/span>。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第六十一条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>&nbsp;\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行对我国其它商业银行债权的风险权重为<span>25%<\/span>，其中原始期限三个月以内（含）债权的风险权重为<span>20%<\/span>。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>&nbsp;<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">以风险权重为<span>0%<\/span>的金融资产作为质押的债权，其覆盖部分的风险权重为<span>0%<\/span>。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行对我国其它商业银行的次级债权（未扣除部分）的风险权重为<span>100%<\/span>。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第六十二条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>&nbsp;\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行对我国其它金融机构债权的风险权重为<span>100%<\/span>。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第六十三条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>&nbsp;\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行对一般企业债权的风险权重为<span>100%<\/span>。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第六十四条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>&nbsp;\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行对同时符合以下条件的微型和小型企业债权的风险权重为<span>75%<\/span>：<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（一）企业符合国家相关部门规定的微型和小型企业认定标准。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（二）商业银行对单家企业（或企业集团）的风险暴露不超过<span>500<\/span>万元。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（三）商业银行对单家企业（或企业集团）的风险<span>暴露占<\/span>本行信用风险暴露总额的比例不高于<span>0.5%<\/span>。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第六十五条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>&nbsp;\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行对个人债权的风险权重。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（一）个人住房抵押贷款的风险权重为<span>50%<\/span>。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（二）对已抵押房产，在购房人没有全部归还贷款前，商业银行以再评估后的净值为抵押追加贷款的，追加部分的风险权重为<span>150%<\/span>。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（三）对个人其它债权的风险权重为<span>75%<\/span>。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第六十六条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>&nbsp;\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">租赁业务的租赁资产余值的风险权重为<span>100%<\/span>。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第六十七条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>&nbsp;\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">下列资产适用<span>250%<\/span>风险权重：<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（一）对金融机构的股权投资（未扣除部分）。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（二）依赖于银行未来盈利的<span>净递延税<\/span>资产（未扣除部分）。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第六十八条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>&nbsp;\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行对工商企业股权投资的风险权重。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（一）商业银行被动持有的对工商企业股权投资在法律规定处分期限内的风险权重为<span>400%<\/span>。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（二）商业银行因政策性原因并经国务院特别批准的对工商企业股权投资的风险权重为<span>400%<\/span>。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（三）商业银行对工商企业其它股权投资的风险权重为<span>1250%<\/span>。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第六十九条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>&nbsp;\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行非自用不动产的风险权重为<span>1250%<\/span>。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行因行使抵押权而持有的非自用不动产在法律规定处分期限内的风险权重为<span>100%<\/span>。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第七十条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>&nbsp;\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行其它资产的风险权重为<span>100%<\/span>。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第七十一条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>&nbsp;\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行各类表外项目的信用转换系数。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（一）等同于贷款的授信业务的信用转换系数为<span>100%<\/span>。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（二）原始期限不超过<span>1<\/span>年和<span>1<\/span>年以上的贷款承诺的信用转换系数分别为<span>20%<\/span>和<span>50%<\/span>；可随时无条件撤销的贷款承诺的信用转换系数为<span>0%<\/span>。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（三）未使用的信用卡授信额度的信用转换系数为<span>50%<\/span>，但同时符合以下条件的未使用的信用卡授信额度的信用转换系数为<span>20%<\/span>：<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">1.<\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">授信对象为自然人，授信方式为无担保循环授信。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">2.<\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">对同一持卡人的授信额度不超过<span>100<\/span>万人民币。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">3.<\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行应至少每年一次评估持卡人的信用程度，按季监控授信额度的使用情况；若持卡人信用状况恶化，商业银行有权降低甚至取消授信额度。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（四）票据发行便利和循环认购便利的信用转换系数为<span>50%<\/span>。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（五）银行借出的证券或用作抵押物的证券，包括回购交易中的证券借贷，信用转换系数为<span>100%<\/span>。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（六） 与贸易直接相关的短期或有项目，信用转换系数为<span>20%<\/span>。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（七）与交易直接相关的或有项目，信用转换系数为<span>50%<\/span>。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（八）信用风险仍在银行的资产销售与购买协议，信用转换系数为<span>100%<\/span>。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（九）远期资产购买、远期定期存款、部分交款的股票及证券，信用转换系数为<span>100%<\/span>。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（十）其它表外项目的信用转换系数均为<span>100%<\/span>。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第七十二条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>&nbsp;\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行应当按照本办法附件<span>2<\/span>的规定对因证券、商品、外汇清算形成的风险暴露计量信用风险加权资产。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第七十三条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>&nbsp;\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行采用权重法计量信用风险加权资产时，可按照本办法附件<span>2<\/span>的规定考虑合格<span>质物质押<\/span>或合格保证主体提供保证的风险缓释作用。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">合格<span>质物质押<\/span>的债权（含证券融资类交易形成的债权），取得与质物相同的风险权重，或取得对质物发行人或承兑人直接债权的风险权重。部分质押的债权（含证券融资类交易形成的债权），受质物保护的部分获得相应的较低风险权重。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">合格保证主体提供全额保证的贷款，取得对保证人直接债权的风险权重。部分保证的贷款，被保证部分获得相应的较低风险权重。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第七十四条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>&nbsp;\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行采用权重法的，质物或保证的担保期限短于被担保债权期限的，不具备风险缓释作用。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span>&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><b><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;\">第三节\r\n内部评级法<span><\/span><\/span><\/b><\/p>\r\n<p><span>&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第七十五条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>&nbsp;\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行应对银行账户信用风险暴露进行分类，并至少分为以下六类：<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（一）主权风险暴露。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（二）金融机构风险暴露，包括银行类金融机构风险暴露和非银行类金融机构风险暴露。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（三）公司风险暴露，包括中小企业风险暴露、专业贷款和一般公司风险暴露。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（四）零售风险暴露，包括个人住房抵押贷款、合格循环零售风险暴露和其它零售风险暴露。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（五）股权风险暴露。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（六）其它风险暴露，包括购入应收款及资产证券化风险暴露。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">主权风险暴露、金融机构风险暴露和公司风险暴露统称为非零售风险暴露。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第七十六条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>&nbsp;\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行应分别计量未违约和已违约风险暴露的风险加权资产：<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（一）未违约非零售风险暴露的风险加权资产计量基于单笔信用风险暴露的违约概率、违约损失率、违约风险暴露、相关性和有效期限。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">未违约零售类风险暴露的风险加权资产计量基于单个资产<span>池风险<\/span>暴露的违约概率、违约损失率、违约风险暴露和相关性。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（二）已违约风险暴露的风险加权资产计量基于违约损失率、预期损失率和违约风险暴露。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第七十七条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>&nbsp;\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行应当按照以下方法确定违约概率：<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（一）主权风险暴露的违约概率为商业银行内部估计的<span>1<\/span>年期违约概率。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（二）公司、金融机构和零售风险暴露的违约概率为商业银行内部估计的<span>1<\/span>年期违约概率与<span>0.03<\/span>％中的较大值。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（三）对于提供合格保证或信用衍生工具的风险暴露，商业银行可以使用保证人的违约概率替代债务人的违约概率。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第七十八条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>&nbsp;\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行应当按照以下方法确定违约损失率：<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（一）商业银行采用初级内部评级法，非零售风险暴露中没有合格抵质押品的高级债权和次级债权的违约损失率分别为<span>45<\/span>％和<span>75<\/span>％。对于提供合格抵质押品的高级债权和从属于净额结算主协议的回购交易，商业银行可以根据风险缓释效应调整违约损失率。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（二）商业银行采用高级内部评级法，应使用内部估计的单笔非零售风险暴露的违约损失率。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（三）商业银行应使用内部估计的零售资产池的违约损失率。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第七十九条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>&nbsp;\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行应当按照以下方法确定违约风险暴露：<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">违约风险暴露应不考虑专项准备和部分核销的影响。表内资产的违约风险暴露应不小于以下两项之和：（<span>1<\/span>）违约风险暴露被完全核销后，银行监管资本下降的数量；（<span>2<\/span>）各项专项准备金和部分核销的数量。如果商业银行估计的违约风险暴露超过以上两项之和，超过部分可视为折扣。风险加权资产的计量不受该折扣的影响，但比较预期损失和合格准备金时，可将该折扣计入准备金。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（一）商业银行采用初级内部评级法，应当按风险暴露名义金额计量表内资产的违约风险暴露，但可以考虑合格净额结算的风险缓释效应。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（二）商业银行采用初级内部评级法，贷款承诺、票据发行便利、循环认购便利等表外项目的信用转换系数为<span>75%<\/span>；可随时无条件撤销的贷款承诺信用转换系数为<span>0%<\/span>；其它各类表外项目的信用转换系数按照本办法第七十一条的规定。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（三）商业银行采用高级内部评级法，应当使用内部估计的非零售违约风险暴露。对于按照本办法第七十一条规定信用转换系数为<span>100%<\/span>的表外项目，应使用<span>100%<\/span>的信用转换系数估计违约风险暴露。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（四）商业银行应当使用内部估计的零售违约风险暴露。对于表外零售风险暴露，商业银行应按照内部估计的信用转换系数计量违约风险暴露。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第八十条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>&nbsp;\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行应当按照以下方法确定有效期限：<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（一）商业银行采用初级内部评级法，非零售风险暴露的有效期限为<span>2.5<\/span>年。回购类交易的有效期限为<span>0.5<\/span>年。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（二）商业银行采用高级内部评级法，有效期限为<span>1<\/span>年和内部估计的有效期限两者之间的较大值，但最大不超过<span>5<\/span>年。中小企业风险暴露的有效期限可以采用<span>2.5<\/span>年。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（三）对于下列短期风险暴露，有效期限为内部估计的有效期限与<span>1<\/span>天中的较大值：<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">1<\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">．原始期限<span>1<\/span>年以内全额抵押的场外衍生品交易、保证金贷款、回购交易和证券借贷交易。交易文件中必须包括按日重新估值并调整保证金，且在交易对手违约或未能补足保证金时可以及时平仓或处置抵押品的条款。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">2.<\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">原始期限<span>1<\/span>年以内自我清偿性的贸易融资，包括开立的和保兑的信用证。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">3.<\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">原始期限<span>3<\/span>个月以内的其它短期风险暴露，包括：场外衍生品交易、保证金贷款、回购交易、证券借贷，短期贷款和存款，证券和外汇清算而产生的风险暴露，以电汇方式进行现金清算产生的风险暴露等。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p><div align=\"right\"><table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\r\n<tr><td class=\"doc_sign\" align=\"center\"><img data-baiduimageplus-ignore src=\"http://icons.xici.net/u16386958/files/sign.pic\"><\/td><\/tr>\r\n<tr><td class=\"doc_sign\" align=\"center\">\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\"><tr><td class=\"doc_sign\">我的名片：<br>\r\n创建紫金家园，打造职场互动沟通平台；<br>\r\n关注基层民声，创造健康和谐企业氛围；<br>\r\n南京拍客（摄影）：我是南京人，传播真善美！&nbsp;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n本版腾讯微博：http://t.qq.com/zijibank<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;新浪微博：http://weibo.com/jszjrcbank<br>\r\n<\/td><\/tr><\/table>\r\n<\/td><\/tr>\r\n<tr><td class=\"doc_sign\" align=\"center\"><a href=\"http://b1123492.xici.net\" target=\"_blank\">紫金家园<\/a><\/td><\/tr>\r\n<\/table><\/div><\/div>\r\n","isAdminFlag":false,"isCanUpdate":false,"isDel":0,"isHide":0,"isShow":true,"keyThis":"","lDocModifiedCount":1,"LongDate":"12-07-01 22:38","online":false,"really_updated_at":"2012-07-01 22:38:07","ShortDate":"07-01 22:38","ShortDate_i":[],"Url":"/d172277779.u16386958.htm","UserID":16386958,"UserName":"富民强企","UseVote":false,"v_isAdminDeleted":false,"v_isAppend":false,"v_isEditOwnDoc":false,"v_lDocModifiedPageNo":0,"v_lDocNo":3,"v_lPageCount":1.00000000000000000e+000,"v_lUserID":0,"v_lUserLevel":100,"v_SeeUserId":0},"isfirstfloor":false},{"docinfo":{},"foolrinfo":{"del_w":false,"DelTime":"","Emote":0,"fd_1_sel_product":false,"fd_id":0,"floorcontent":"<div class=doc_txt  id=\"text_5_0\"><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><span style=\"font-family:黑体;\">第五章<span><span>&nbsp;\r\n<\/span><\/span>市场风险加权资产计量<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span>&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><b><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;\">第一节\r\n一般规定<span><\/span><\/span><\/b><\/p>\r\n<p><span>&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第八十一条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>&nbsp;\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">本办法所称市场风险是指因市场价格（利率、汇率、股票价格和商品价格）的不利变动而使商业银行表内和表外业务发生损失的风险。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第八十二条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>&nbsp;\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">市场风险资本计量应覆盖商业银行交易账户中的利率风险和股票风险，以及<span>全部汇率<\/span>风险和商品风险。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行可以不对结构性外汇风险暴露计提市场风险资本。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第八十三条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>&nbsp;\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">本办法所称交易账户包括为交易目的或对冲交易账户其它项目的风险而持有的金融工具和商品头寸。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">前款所称为交易目的而持有的头寸是指短期内有目的地持有以便出售，或从实际或预期的短期价格波动中获利，或锁定套利的头寸，包括自营业务、做<span>市业务<\/span>和为执行客户买卖委托的代客业务而持有的头寸。交易账户中的金融工具和商品头寸原则上还应满足以下条件：<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（一）在交易方面不受任何限制，可以随时平盘。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（二）能够完全对冲以规避风险。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（三）能够准确估值。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（四）能够进行积极的管理。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第八十四条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>&nbsp;\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行应当制定清晰的银行账户和交易账户划分标准，明确纳入交易账户的金融工具和商品头寸以及在银行账户和交易账户间划转的条件，确保执行的一致性。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第八十五条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>&nbsp;\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行可以采用标准法或内部模型法计量市场风险资本要求。未经银监会核准，商业银行不得变更市场风险资本计量方法。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第八十六条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>&nbsp;\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行采用内部模型法<span>,<\/span>若未覆盖所有市场风险，<span>经银监<\/span>会核准，可组合采用内部模型法和标准法计量市场风险资本要求，但银行集团内部同一机构不得对同一种市场风险采用不同方法计量市场风险资本要求。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第八十七条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>&nbsp;\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行采用内部模型法，内部模型法覆盖率应不低于<span>50%<\/span>。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">前款所称内部模型法覆盖率按以下公式确定：<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">内部模型法覆盖率<span>=<\/span>按内部模型法计量的资本要求<span>/<\/span>（按内部模型法计量的资本要求＋按标准法计量的资本要求）×<span>100%<\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第八十八条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>&nbsp;\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行市场风险加权资产为市场风险资本要求的<span>12.5<\/span>倍，即：市场风险加权资产<span>=<\/span>市场风险资本要求×<span>12.5<\/span>。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span>&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><b><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;\">第二节\r\n标准法<span><\/span><\/span><\/b><\/p>\r\n<p><span>&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第八十九条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>&nbsp;\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行采用标准法，应当按照本办法附件<span>10<\/span>的规定分别计量利率风险、汇率风险、商品风险和股票风险的资本要求，并单独计量以各类风险为基础的期权风险的资本要求。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第九十条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>&nbsp;\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">市场风险资本要求为利率风险、汇率风险、商品风险、股票风险和期权风险的资本要求之<span>和<\/span>。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">利率风险资本要求和股票风险资本要求为一般市场风险资本要求和特定风险资本要求之<span>和<\/span>。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span>&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><b><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;\">第三节\r\n内部模型法<span><\/span><\/span><\/b><\/p>\r\n<p><span>&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第九十一条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>&nbsp;\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行采用内部模型法的，应当符合本办法附件<span>11<\/span>的规定，<span>并经银监<\/span>会核准。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第九十二条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>&nbsp;\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行采用内部模型法，其一般市场风险资本要求为一般风险价值与压力风险价值之和，即：<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">K = Max<\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（<span>VaRt-1\r\n<\/span>，<span> mc<\/span>×<span>VaRavg<\/span>）<span>+Max<\/span>（<span>sVaRt-1<\/span>，<span>mS<\/span>×<span>sVaRavg<\/span>）<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">其中：<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（一）<span>VaR<\/span>为一般风险价值，为以下两项中的较大值：<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">1.<\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">根据内部模型计量的上一交易日的风险价值（<span>VaRt-1<\/span>）。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">2.<\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">最近<span>60<\/span>个交易<span>日风险<\/span>价值的均值（<span>VaRavg<\/span>）乘以<span>mC<\/span>。<span>mC<\/span>最小为<span>3<\/span>，根据返回检验的突破次数可以增加附加因子。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（二）<span>sVaR<\/span>为压力风险价值，为以下两项中的较大值：<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">1.<\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">根据内部模型计量的上一交易日的压力风险价值（<span>sVaRt-1<\/span>）。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">2.<\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">最近<span>60<\/span>个交易<span>日压力<\/span>风险价值的均值（<span>sVaRavg<\/span>）乘以<span>ms<\/span>。<span>\r\nms<\/span>最小为<span>3<\/span>。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第九十三条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>&nbsp;\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行采用内部模型法计量特定风险资本要求的，应当按照本办法附件<span>11<\/span>的规定使用内部模型计量新增风险资本要求。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行内部模型未达到计量特定市场风险要求的合格标准，或内部模型未覆盖新增风险，应当按标准法计量特定市场风险资本要求。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p><div align=\"right\"><table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\r\n<tr><td class=\"doc_sign\" align=\"center\"><img data-baiduimageplus-ignore src=\"http://icons.xici.net/u16386958/files/sign.pic\"><\/td><\/tr>\r\n<tr><td class=\"doc_sign\" align=\"center\">\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\"><tr><td class=\"doc_sign\">我的名片：<br>\r\n创建紫金家园，打造职场互动沟通平台；<br>\r\n关注基层民声，创造健康和谐企业氛围；<br>\r\n南京拍客（摄影）：我是南京人，传播真善美！&nbsp;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n本版腾讯微博：http://t.qq.com/zijibank<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;新浪微博：http://weibo.com/jszjrcbank<br>\r\n<\/td><\/tr><\/table>\r\n<\/td><\/tr>\r\n<tr><td class=\"doc_sign\" align=\"center\"><a href=\"http://b1123492.xici.net\" target=\"_blank\">紫金家园<\/a><\/td><\/tr>\r\n<\/table><\/div><\/div>\r\n","isAdminFlag":false,"isCanUpdate":false,"isDel":0,"isHide":0,"isShow":true,"keyThis":"","lDocModifiedCount":1,"LongDate":"12-07-01 22:38","online":false,"really_updated_at":"2012-07-01 22:38:41","ShortDate":"07-01 22:38","ShortDate_i":[],"Url":"/d172277779.u16386958.htm","UserID":16386958,"UserName":"富民强企","UseVote":false,"v_isAdminDeleted":false,"v_isAppend":false,"v_isEditOwnDoc":false,"v_lDocModifiedPageNo":0,"v_lDocNo":4,"v_lPageCount":1.00000000000000000e+000,"v_lUserID":0,"v_lUserLevel":100,"v_SeeUserId":0},"isfirstfloor":false},{"docinfo":{},"foolrinfo":{"del_w":false,"DelTime":"","Emote":0,"fd_1_sel_product":false,"fd_id":0,"floorcontent":"<div class=doc_txt  id=\"text_6_0\"><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><span style=\"font-family:黑体;\">第六章<span><span>&nbsp;\r\n<\/span><\/span>操作风险加权资产计量<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span>&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><b><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;\">第一节\r\n一般规定<span><\/span><\/span><\/b><\/p>\r\n<p><span>&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第九十四条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>&nbsp;\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">本办法所称的操作风险是指由不完善或有问题的内部程序、员工和信息科技系统，以及外部事件所造成损失的风险，包括法律风险，但不包括策略风险和声誉风险。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第九十五条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>&nbsp;\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行可采用基本指标法、标准法或高级计量法计量操作风险资本要求。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行采用标准法或高级计量法计量操作风险资本要求，应符合本办法附件<span>12<\/span>的规定，<span>并经银监<\/span>会核准。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">未经银监会核准，商业银行不得变更操作风险资本计量方法。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第九十六条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>&nbsp;\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行操作风险加权资产为操作风险资本要求的<span>12.5<\/span>倍，即：操作风险加权资产<span>=<\/span>操作风险资本要求×<span>12.5<\/span>。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span>&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><b><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;\">第二节\r\n基本指标法<span><\/span><\/span><\/b><\/p>\r\n<p><span>&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第九十七条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>&nbsp;\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行采用基本指标法，应当以总收入为基础计量操作风险资本要求。商业银行应当按照本办法附件<span>12<\/span>的规定确认总收入。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">总收入为净利息收入<span>与净非利息收入<\/span>之<span>和<\/span>。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第九十八条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>&nbsp;\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行采用基本指标法，应当按照以下公式计量操作风险资本要求：<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>&nbsp;<\/span><\/span><sub><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"> <\/span><\/sub><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">其中：<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">KBIA<\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">为按基本指标法计量的操作风险资本要求。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">GI<\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">为过去三年中每年正的总收入。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">n<\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">为过去三年中总收入为正的年数。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">α为<span>15%<\/span>。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span>&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><b><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;\">第三节\r\n标准法<span><\/span><\/span><\/b><\/p>\r\n<p><span>&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第九十九条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>&nbsp;\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行采用标准法，应当以各业务条线的总收入为基础计量操作风险资本要求。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第一百条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>&nbsp;\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行采用标准法，应当按照本办法附件<span>12<\/span>的规定将全部业务划分为公司金融、交易和销售、零售银行、商业银行、支付和清算、代理服务、资产管理、零售经纪和其它业务等<span>9<\/span>个业务条线。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第一百零一条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行采用标准法，应当按照以下公式计量操作风险资本要求：<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height:24pt;text-indent:21pt;\"><span><span>&nbsp;<\/span><\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><sub> <\/sub><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height:24pt;text-indent:30pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">其中<span>:\r\n<\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height:24pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt 0.05pt;text-indent:38.1pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">K<sub>TSA <\/sub><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">为按标准法计量的操作风险资本要求。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height:24pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-indent:21.9pt;\"><span><sub><\/sub><\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">是指各年为正的操作风险资本要求。<\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height:24pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-indent:29.85pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">GI<sub>i<\/sub><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">为各业务条线总收入。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height:24pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-indent:29.85pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:Symbol;\"><span>b<\/span><\/span><sub><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">i<\/span><\/sub><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">为各业务条线的操作风险资本系数。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span>&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第一百零二条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">各业务条线的操作风险资本系数（β）如下：<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（一）零售银行、资产管理和零售经纪业务条线的操作风险资本系数为<span>12%<\/span>。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（二）商业银行和代理服务业务条线的操作风险资本系数为<span>15%<\/span>。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（三）公司金融、支付和清算、交易和销售以及其它业务条线的操作风险资本系数为<span>18%<\/span>。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span>&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><b><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;\">第四节\r\n高级计量法<span><\/span><\/span><\/b><\/p>\r\n<p><span>&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第一百零三条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行采用高级计量法，可根据业务性质、规模和产品复杂程度以及风险管理水平选择操作风险计量模型。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第一百零四条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行采用高级计量法，应当基于内部损失数据、外部损失数据、情景分析、业务经营环境和内部控制因素建立操作风险计量模型。建立模型使用的内部损失数据应充分反映本行操作风险的实际情况。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p><div align=\"right\"><table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\r\n<tr><td class=\"doc_sign\" align=\"center\"><img data-baiduimageplus-ignore src=\"http://icons.xici.net/u16386958/files/sign.pic\"><\/td><\/tr>\r\n<tr><td class=\"doc_sign\" align=\"center\">\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\"><tr><td class=\"doc_sign\">我的名片：<br>\r\n创建紫金家园，打造职场互动沟通平台；<br>\r\n关注基层民声，创造健康和谐企业氛围；<br>\r\n南京拍客（摄影）：我是南京人，传播真善美！&nbsp;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n本版腾讯微博：http://t.qq.com/zijibank<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;新浪微博：http://weibo.com/jszjrcbank<br>\r\n<\/td><\/tr><\/table>\r\n<\/td><\/tr>\r\n<tr><td class=\"doc_sign\" align=\"center\"><a href=\"http://b1123492.xici.net\" target=\"_blank\">紫金家园<\/a><\/td><\/tr>\r\n<\/table><\/div><\/div>\r\n","isAdminFlag":false,"isCanUpdate":false,"isDel":0,"isHide":0,"isShow":true,"keyThis":"","lDocModifiedCount":1,"LongDate":"12-07-01 22:39","online":false,"really_updated_at":"2012-07-01 22:39:37","ShortDate":"07-01 22:39","ShortDate_i":[],"Url":"/d172277779.u16386958.htm","UserID":16386958,"UserName":"富民强企","UseVote":false,"v_isAdminDeleted":false,"v_isAppend":false,"v_isEditOwnDoc":false,"v_lDocModifiedPageNo":0,"v_lDocNo":5,"v_lPageCount":1.00000000000000000e+000,"v_lUserID":0,"v_lUserLevel":100,"v_SeeUserId":0},"isfirstfloor":false},{"docinfo":{},"foolrinfo":{"del_w":false,"DelTime":"","Emote":0,"fd_1_sel_product":false,"fd_id":0,"floorcontent":"<div class=doc_txt  id=\"text_7_0\"><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><span style=\"font-family:黑体;\">第七章<span><span>&nbsp;\r\n<\/span><\/span>商业银行内部资本充足评估程序<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span>&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><b><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;\">第一节\r\n一般规定<span><\/span><\/span><\/b><\/p>\r\n<p><span>&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第一百零五条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行应当建立完善的风险管理框架和稳健的内部资本充足评估程序，明确风险治理结构，审慎评估各类风险、资本充足水平和资本质量，制定资本规划和资本充足率管理计划，确保银行资本能够充分抵御其所面临的风险，满足业务发展的需要。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第一百零六条<span><span> <\/span><\/span><\/span><\/b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行内部资本充足评估程序应实现以下目标：<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（一）确保主要风险得到识别、计量或评估、监测和报告。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（二）确保资本水平与风险偏好及风险管理水平相适应。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（三）确保资本规划与银行经营状况、风险变化趋势及长期发展战略相匹配。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第一百零七条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行应当将压力测试作为内部资本充足评估程序的重要组成部分，结合压力测试结果确定内部资本充足率目标。压力测试应覆盖各业务条线的主要风险，并充分考虑经济周期对资本充足率的影响。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第一百零八条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行应当将内部资本充足评估程序作为内部管理和决策的组成部分，并将内部资本充足评估结果运用于资本预算与分配、授<span>信决策<\/span>和战略规划。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第一百零九条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行应当制定合理的薪酬政策，确保薪酬水平、结构和发放时间安排与风险大小和风险存续期限一致，反映风险调整后的长期收益水平，防止过度承担风险，维护财务稳健性。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第一百一十条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行应当至少每年一次实施内部资本充足评估程序，在银行经营情况、风险状况和外部环境发生重大变化时，应及时进行调整和更新。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span>&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><b><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;\">第二节\r\n治理结构<span><\/span><\/span><\/b><\/p>\r\n<p><span>&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第一百一十一条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行董事会承担本行资本管理的首要责任，履行以下职责：<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（一）设定与银行发展战略和外部环境相适应的风险偏好和资本充足目标，审批银行内部资本充足评估程序，确保资本充分覆盖主要风险。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（二）审批资本管理制度，确保资本管理政策和控制措施有效。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（三）监督内部资本充足评估程序的全面性、前瞻性和有效性。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（四）审批并监督资本规划的实施，满足银行持续经营和应急性资本补充需要。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（五）至少每年一次审批资本充足率管理计划，审议资本充足率管理报告及内部资本充足评估报告，听取对资本充足率管理和内部资本充足评估程序执行情况的审计报告。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（六）审批资本充足<span>率信息<\/span>披露政策、程序和内容，并保证披露信息的真实、准确和完整。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（七）确保商业银行有足够的资源，能够独立、有效地开展资本管理工作。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第一百一十二条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行采用资本计量高级方法的，董事会还应负责审批资本计量高级方法的管理体系实施规划和重大管理政策，监督高级管理层制定并实施资本计量高级方法的管理政策和流程，确保商业银行有足够资源支持资本计量高级方法管理体系的运行。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第一百一十三条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行高级管理<span>层负责<\/span>根据业务战略和风险偏好组织实施资本管理工作，确保资本与业务发展、风险水平相适应，落实各项监控措施。具体履行以下职责：<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（一）制定并组织执行资本管理的规章制度。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（二）制定并组织实施内部资本充足评估程序，明确相关部门的职责分工，建立健全评估框架、流程和管理制度，确保与商业银行全面风险管理、资本计量及分配等保持一致。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（三）制定和组织实施资本规划和资本充足率管理计划。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（四）定期和不定期评估资本充足率，向董事会报告资本充足率水平、资本充足率管理情况和内部资本充足评估结果。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（五）组织开展压力测试，参与压力测试目标、方案及重要假设的确定，推动压力测试结果在风险评估和资本规划中的运用，确保资本应急补充机制的有效性。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（六）组织内部资本充足评估信息管理系统的开发和维护工作，确保信息管理系统及时、准确地提供评估所需信息。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第一百一十四条<span><span> <\/span><\/span><\/span><\/b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行采用资本计量高级方法的，高级管理层还应定期评估方法和工具的合理性和有效性，定期听取资本计量高级方法验证工作的汇报，履行资本计量高级方法体系的建设、验证和持续优化等职责。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第一百一十五条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行监事会应当对董事会及高级管理层在资本管理和资本计量高级方法管理中的履职情况进行监督评价，并至少每年一次向股东大会报告董事会及高级管理层的履职情况。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第一百一十六条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行应当指定相关部门履行以下资本管理职责：<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（一）制定资本总量、结构和质量管理计划，编制并实施资本规划和资本充足率管理计划，向高级管理<span>层报告<\/span>资本规划和资本充足率管理计划执行情况。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（二）持续监控并定期测算资本充足率水平，开展资本充足<span>率压力<\/span>测试。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（三）组织建立内部资本计量、配置和风险调整资本收益的评价管理体系。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（四）组织实施内部资本充足评估程序。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（五）建立资本应急补充机制，参与或组织筹集资本。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（六）编制或参与编制资本充足<span>率信息<\/span>披露文件。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第一百一十七条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行采用资本计量高级方法的，相关部门还应履行以下职责：<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（一）设计、实施、监控和维护资本计量高级方法。<span> <\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（二）健全资本计量高级方法管理机制。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（三）向高级管理<span>层报告<\/span>资本计量高级方法的计量结果。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（四）组织开展各类风险压力测试。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第一百一十八条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行采用资本计量高级方法的，应当建立验证部门（团队），负责资本计量高级方法的验证工作。验证部门（团队）应独立于资本计量高级方法的开发和运行部门（团队）。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第一百一十九条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行应当明确内部审计部门在资本管理中的职责。内部审计部门应当履行以下职责：<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（一）评估资本管理的治理结构和相关部门履职情况，以及相关人员的专业技能和资源充分性。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（二）至少每年一次检查内部资本充足评估程序相关政策和执行情况。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（三）至少每年一次评估资本规划的执行情况。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（四）至少每年一次评估资本充足率管理计划的执行情况。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（五）检查资本管理的信息系统和数据管理的合<span>规<\/span>性和有效性。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（六）向董事会提交资本充足率管理审计报告、内部资本充足评估程序执行情况审计报告、资本计量高级方法管理审计报告。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第一百二十条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行采用资本计量高级方法的，内部审计部门还应评估资本计量高级方法的适用性和有效性，检查计量结果的可靠性和准确性，检查资本计量高级方法的验证政策和程序，评估验证工作的独立性和有效性。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span>&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><b><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;\">第三节\r\n风险评估<span><\/span><\/span><\/b><\/p>\r\n<p><span>&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第一百二十一条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行应当按照银监会相关要求和本办法附件<span>13<\/span>的规定，设立主要风险的识别和评估标准，确保主要风险得到及时识别、审慎评估和有效监控。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">主要风险包括可能导致重大损失的单一风险，以及单一风险程度不高、但与其它风险相互作用可能导致重大损失的风险。风险评估应至少覆盖以下各类风险：<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（一）本办法第四章、第五章和第六章中涉及且已覆盖的风险，包括信用风险、市场风险和操作风险。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（二）本办法第四章、第五章和第六章中涉及但没有完全覆盖的风险，包括集中度风险、剩余操作风险等。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（三）本办法第四章、第五章和第六章中未涉及的风险，包括银行账户利率风险、流动性风险、声誉风险、战略风险和对商业银行有实质性影响的其它风险。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（四）外部经营环境变化引发的风险。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第一百二十二条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行应当有效评估和管理各类主要风险。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（一）对能够量化的风险，商业银行应当开发和完善风险计量技术，确保风险计量的一致性、客观性和准确性，在此基础上加强对相关风险的缓释、控制和管理。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（二）对难以量化的风险，商业银行应当建立风险识别、评估、控制和报告机制，确保相关风险得到有效管理。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第一百二十三条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行应当建立风险加总的政策和程序，确保在不同层次上及时识别风险。商业银行可以采用多种风险加总方法，但应至少采取简单加总法，并判断风险加总结果的合理性和审慎性。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第一百二十四条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行进行风险加总，应当充分考虑集中度风险及风险之间的相互传染。若考虑风险分散化效应，应基于长期实证数据，<span>且数据<\/span>观察期至少覆盖一个完整的经济周期。否则，商业银行应对风险加总方法和假设进行审慎调整。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span>&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><b><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;\">第四节\r\n资本规划<span><\/span><\/span><\/b><\/p>\r\n<p><span>&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第一百二十五条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行制定资本规划，应当综合考虑风险评估结果、未来资本需求、资本监管要求和资本可获得性，确保资本水平持续满足监管要求。资本规划应至少设定内部资本充足率三年目标。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第一百二十六条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行制定资本规划，应当确保目标资本水平与业务发展战略、风险偏好、风险管理水平和外部经营环境相适应，兼顾短期和长期资本需求，并考虑各种资本补充来源的长期可持续性。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第一百二十七条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行制定资本规划，应当审慎估计资产质量、利润增长及资本市场的波动性，充分考虑对银行资本水平可能产生重大负面影响的因素，包括或有风险暴露，严重且长期的市场衰退，以及突破风险承受能力的其它事件。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第一百二十八条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行应当优先考虑补充核心一级资本，增强内部资本积累能力，完善资本结构，提高资本质量。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第一百二十九条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行应当通过严格和前瞻性的压力测试，测算不同压力条件下的资本需求和资本可获得性，并制定资本应急预案以满足计划外的资本需求，确保银行具备充足资本应对不利的市场条件变化。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">对于重度压力测试结果，商业银行应当在应急预案中明确相应的资本补充政策安排和应对措施，并充分考虑融资市场流动性变化，合理设计资本补充渠道。商业银行的资本应急预案应包括紧急筹资成本分析和可行性分析、限制资本占用程度高的业务发展、采用风险缓释措施等。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行高级管理层应当充分理解压力条件下商业银行所面临的风险及风险间的相互作用、资本工具吸收损失和支持业务持续运营的能力，并判断资本管理目标、资本补充政策安排和应对措施的合理性。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><b><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/b><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><b><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;\">第五节\r\n监测和报告<span><\/span><\/span><\/b><\/p>\r\n<p><span>&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第一百三十条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行应当建立内部资本充足评估程序的报告体系，定期监测和报告银行资本水平和主要影响因素的变化趋势。报告应至少包括以下内容：<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（一）评估主要风险状况及发展趋势、战略目标和外部环境对资本水平的影响。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（二）评估实际持有的资本是否足以抵御主要风险。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（三）提出确保资本能够充分覆盖主要风险的建议。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">根据重要性和报告用途不同，商业银行应当明确各<span>类报告<\/span>的发送范围、报告内容及详略程度，确保报告信息与报送频率满足银行资本管理的需要。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第一百三十一条<span><span> <\/span><\/span><\/span><\/b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行应当建立用于风险和资本的计量和管理的信息管理系统。商业银行的信息管理系统应具备以下功能：<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（一）清晰、及时地向董事会和高级管理层提供总体风险信息。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（二）准确、及时地加总各业务条线的风险暴露和风险计量结果。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（三）动态支持集中度风险和潜在风险的识别。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（四）识别、计量并管理各类风险缓释工具以及因风险缓释带来的风险。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（五）为多角度评估风险计量的不确定性提供支持，分析潜在风险假设条件变化带来的影响。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（六）支持前瞻性的情景分析，评估市场变化和压力情形对银行资本的影响。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（七）监测、报告风险限额的执行情况。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第一百三十二条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行应当系统性地收集、整理、跟踪和分析各类风险相关数据，建立数据仓库、风险数据集市和数据管理系统，以获取、清洗、转换和存储数据，并建立数据质量控制政策和程序，确保数据的完整性、全面性、准确性和一致性，满足资本计量和内部资本充足评估等工作的需要。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第一百三十三条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行的数据管理系统应当达到资本<span>充足率非现场<\/span>监管报表和资本充足<span>率信息<\/span>披露的有关要求。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第一百三十四条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行应当建立完整的文档管理平台，为内部审计部门及银监会对资本管理的评估提供支持。文档应至少包括：<span>\r\n<\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（一）董事会、高级管理层和相关部门的职责、独立性以及履职情况。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（二）关于资本管理、风险管理等政策流程的制度文件。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（三）资本规划、资本充足率管理计划、内部资本充足评估报告、风险计量模型验证报告、压力测试报告、审计报告以及上述报告的相关重要文档。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（四）关于资本管理的会议纪要和重要决策意见。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p><div align=\"right\"><table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\r\n<tr><td class=\"doc_sign\" align=\"center\"><img data-baiduimageplus-ignore src=\"http://icons.xici.net/u16386958/files/sign.pic\"><\/td><\/tr>\r\n<tr><td class=\"doc_sign\" align=\"center\">\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\"><tr><td class=\"doc_sign\">我的名片：<br>\r\n创建紫金家园，打造职场互动沟通平台；<br>\r\n关注基层民声，创造健康和谐企业氛围；<br>\r\n南京拍客（摄影）：我是南京人，传播真善美！&nbsp;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n本版腾讯微博：http://t.qq.com/zijibank<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;新浪微博：http://weibo.com/jszjrcbank<br>\r\n<\/td><\/tr><\/table>\r\n<\/td><\/tr>\r\n<tr><td class=\"doc_sign\" align=\"center\"><a href=\"http://b1123492.xici.net\" target=\"_blank\">紫金家园<\/a><\/td><\/tr>\r\n<\/table><\/div><\/div>\r\n","isAdminFlag":false,"isCanUpdate":false,"isDel":0,"isHide":0,"isShow":true,"keyThis":"","lDocModifiedCount":1,"LongDate":"12-07-01 22:40","online":false,"really_updated_at":"2012-07-01 22:40:17","ShortDate":"07-01 22:40","ShortDate_i":[],"Url":"/d172277779.u16386958.htm","UserID":16386958,"UserName":"富民强企","UseVote":false,"v_isAdminDeleted":false,"v_isAppend":false,"v_isEditOwnDoc":false,"v_lDocModifiedPageNo":0,"v_lDocNo":6,"v_lPageCount":1.00000000000000000e+000,"v_lUserID":0,"v_lUserLevel":100,"v_SeeUserId":0},"isfirstfloor":false},{"docinfo":{},"foolrinfo":{"del_w":false,"DelTime":"","Emote":0,"fd_1_sel_product":false,"fd_id":0,"floorcontent":"<div class=doc_txt  id=\"text_8_0\"><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><span style=\"font-family:黑体;\">第八章<span><span>&nbsp;\r\n<\/span><\/span>监督检查<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span>&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><b><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;\">第一节\r\n监督检查内容<span><\/span><\/span><\/b><\/p>\r\n<p><span>&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第一百三十五条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">资本充足<span>率监督<\/span>检查是银监会审慎风险监管体系的重要组成部分。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第一百三十六条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">银监会根据宏观经济运行、产业政策和信贷风险变化，识别银行业重大系统性风险，对相关资产组合提出特定资本要求。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第一百三十七条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">银监会对商业银行实施资本充足<span>率监督<\/span>检查，确保资本能够充分覆盖所面临的各类风险。资本充足<span>率监督<\/span>检查包括但不限于以下内容：<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（一）评估商业银行全面风险管理框架。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（二）审查商业银行对合格资本工具的认定，以及各类风险加权资产的计量方法和结果，评估资本充足率计量结果的合理性和准确性。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（三）检查商业银行内部资本充足评估程序，评估公司治理、资本规划、内部控制和审计等。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（四）对商业银行的信用风险、市场风险、操作风险、银行账户利率风险、流动性风险、声誉风险以及战略风险等各类风险进行评估，并对压力测试工作开展情况进行检查。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第一百三十八条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行采用资本计量高级方法，应按本办法附件<span>14<\/span>的规定向银监会提出申请。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第一百三十九条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">银监会依照本办法附件<span>14<\/span>的规定对商业银行进行评估，根据评估结果决定是否核准商业银行采用资本计量高级方法；并对商业银行资本计量高级方法的使用情况和验证工作进行持续监督检查。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第一百四十条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行不能持续达到本办法规定的资本计量高级方法的运用要求，银监会有权要求其限期整改。商业银行在规定期限内未达标，银监会有权取消其采用资本计量高级方法的资格。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:center;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;\">第二节 监督检查程序<span><\/span><\/span><\/b><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第一百四十一条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">银监会建立资本监管工作机制，履行以下职责：<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（一）评估银行业面临的重大系统性风险，提出针对特定资产组合的第二支柱资本要求的建议。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（二）制定商业银行资本充足<span>率监督<\/span>检查总体规划，协调和督促对商业银行资本充足<span>率监督<\/span>检查的实施。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（三）审议并决定对商业银行的监管资本要求。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（四）受理商业银行就资本充足<span>率监督<\/span>检查结果提出的申辩，确保监督检查过程以及评价结果的公正和准确。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第一百四十二条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">银监会通过非现场监管和现场检查的方式对商业银行资本充足率进行监督检查。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">除对资本充足率的常规监督检查外，银监会可根据商业银行内部情况或外部市场环境的变化实施资本充足率的临时监督检查。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第一百四十三条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行应当在年度结束后的四个月内向银监会提交内部资本充足评估报告。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第一百四十四条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">银监会实施资本充足<span>率监督<\/span>检查应遵循以下程序：<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（一）审查商业银行内部资本充足评估报告，制定资本充足<span>率检查<\/span>计划。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（二）依据本办法附件<span>13<\/span>规定的风险评估标准，实施资本充足<span>率现场<\/span>检查。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（三）根据检查结果初步确定商业银行的监管资本要求。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（四）与商业银行高级管理层就资本充足<span>率检查<\/span>情况进行沟通，并将评价结果书面发送商业银行董事会。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（五）监督商业银行持续满足监管资本要求的情况。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第一百四十五条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行可以在接到资本充足<span>率监督<\/span>检查评价结果后<span>60<\/span>日内，以书面形式向银监会提出申辩。在接到评价结果后<span>60<\/span>日内未进行书面申辩的，将被视为接受评价结果。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行提出书面申辩的，应当提交董事会关于进行申辩的决议，并对申辩理由进行详细说明，同时提交能够证明申辩理由充分性的相关资料。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第一百四十六条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">银监会受理并审查商业银行提交的书面申辩，视情况对有关问题进行重点核查。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">银监会在受理书面申辩后的<span>60<\/span>日内做出是否同意商业银行申辩的书面答复，并说明理由。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第一百四十七条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">银监会审查商业银行的书面申辩期间，商业银行应当执行资本充足<span>率监督<\/span>检查所确定的监管资本要求，并落实银监会采取的相关监管措施。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第一百四十八条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行应当向银监会报告未并表和<span>并<\/span>表后的资本充足率。并表后的资本充足率每半年报送一次，未并表的资本充足率每季报送一次。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">如<span>遇影响<\/span>资本充足率的特别重大事项，商业银行应当及时向银监会报告。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:center;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;\">第三节 第二支柱资本要求<span><\/span><\/span><\/b><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第一百四十九条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行已建立内部资本充足评估程序且评估程序达到本办法要求的，银监会根据其内部资本评估结果确定监管资本要求；商业银行未建立内部资本充足评估程序，或评估程序未达到本办法要求的，银监会根据对商业银行风险状况的评估结果，确定商业银行的监管资本要求。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第一百五十条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">银监会有权根据单家商业银行操作风险管理水平及操作风险事件发生情况，提高操作风险的监管资本要求。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第一百五十一条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">银监会有权通过调整风险权重、相关性系数、有效期限等方法，提高特定资产组合的资本要求，包括但不限于以下内容：<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（一）根据现金流覆盖比例、区域风险差异，确定地方政府融资平台贷款的集中度风险资本要求。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（二）通过期限调整因子，确定中长期贷款的资本要求。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（三）针对贷款行业集中度风险状况，确定部分行业的贷款集中度风险资本要求。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（四）根据个人住房抵押贷款用于购买非自住用房的风险状况，提高个人住房抵押贷款资本要求。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:center;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;\">第四节 监管措施<span><\/span><\/span><\/b><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第一百五十二条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">银监会有权对资本充足率未达到监管要求的商业银行采取监管措施，督促其提高资本充足水平。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第一百五十三条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">根据资本充足状况，银监会将商业银行分为四类：<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（一）第一类商业银行：资本充足率、一级资本充足率和核心一级资本充足率均达到本办法规定的各级资本要求。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（二）第二类商业银行：资本充足率、一级资本充足率和核心一级资本充足率未达到第二支柱资本要求，但均不低于其它各级资本要求。<span>\r\n<\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（三）第三类商业银行：资本充足率、一级资本充足率和核心一级资本充足率均不低于最低资本要求，但未达到其它各级资本要求。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（四）第四类商业银行：资本充足率、一级资本充足率和核心一级资本充足率任意一项未达到最低资本要求。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第一百五十四条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">对第一类商业银行，银监会支持其稳健发展业务。为防止其资本充足率水平快速下降，银监会可以采取下列预警监管措施：<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（一）要求商业银行加强对资本充足率水平下降原因的分析及预测。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（二）要求商业银行制定切实可行的资本充足率管理计划。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（三）要求商业银行提高风险控制能力。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第一百五十五条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">对第二类商业银行，除本办法第一百五十四条规定的监管措施外，银监会还可以采取下列监管措施：<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（一）与商业银行董事会、高级管理层进行审慎性会谈。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（二）下发监管意见书，监管意见书内容包括：商业银行资本管理存在的问题、拟采取的纠正措施和限期达标意见等。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（三）要求商业银行制定切实可行的资本补充计划和限期达标计划。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（四）增加对商业银行资本充足的监督检查频率。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（五）要求商业银行对特定风险领域采取风险缓释措施。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第一百五十六条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">对第三类商业银行，除本办法第一百五十四条、第一百五十五条规定的监管措施外，银监会还可以采取下列监管措施：<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（一）限制商业银行分配红利和其它收入。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（二）限制商业银行向董事、高级管理人员实施任何形式的激励。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（三）限制商业银行进行股权投资或回购资本工具。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（四）限制商业银行重要资本性支出。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（五）要求商业银行控制风险资产增长。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第一百五十七<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">条<span><span>\r\n<\/span><\/span>对第四类商业银行，除本办法第一百五十四条、第一百五十五条和第一百五十六条规定的监管措施外，银监会还可以采取以下监管措施：<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（一）要求商业银行大幅降低风险资产的规模。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（二）责令商业银行停办<span>一切高<\/span>风险资产业务。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（三）限制或禁止商业银行增设新机构、开办新业务。<span> <\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（四）强制要求商业银行对二级资本工具<span>进行减记或<\/span>转为普通股。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（五）责令商业银行调整董事、高级管理人员或限制其权利。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（六）依法对商业银行实行接管或者促成机构重组，直至予以撤销。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">在处置此类商业银行时，银监会还将综合考虑外部因素，采取其它必要措施。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第一百五十八条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行未按本办法规定提供资本充足率报表或报告、未按规定进行信息披露或提供虚假的或者隐瞒重要事实的报表和统计报告的，银监会依据《中华人民共和国银行业监督管理法》的相关规定实施行政处罚。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第一百五十九条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">除上述监管措施外，银监会可依据《中华人民共和国银行业监督管理法》以及相关法律、行政法规和部门规章的规定，采取其它监管措施。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p><div align=\"right\"><table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\r\n<tr><td class=\"doc_sign\" align=\"center\"><img data-baiduimageplus-ignore src=\"http://icons.xici.net/u16386958/files/sign.pic\"><\/td><\/tr>\r\n<tr><td class=\"doc_sign\" align=\"center\">\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\"><tr><td class=\"doc_sign\">我的名片：<br>\r\n创建紫金家园，打造职场互动沟通平台；<br>\r\n关注基层民声，创造健康和谐企业氛围；<br>\r\n南京拍客（摄影）：我是南京人，传播真善美！&nbsp;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n本版腾讯微博：http://t.qq.com/zijibank<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;新浪微博：http://weibo.com/jszjrcbank<br>\r\n<\/td><\/tr><\/table>\r\n<\/td><\/tr>\r\n<tr><td class=\"doc_sign\" align=\"center\"><a href=\"http://b1123492.xici.net\" target=\"_blank\">紫金家园<\/a><\/td><\/tr>\r\n<\/table><\/div><\/div>\r\n","isAdminFlag":false,"isCanUpdate":false,"isDel":0,"isHide":0,"isShow":true,"keyThis":"","lDocModifiedCount":1,"LongDate":"12-07-01 22:41","online":false,"really_updated_at":"2012-07-01 22:41:04","ShortDate":"07-01 22:41","ShortDate_i":[],"Url":"/d172277779.u16386958.htm","UserID":16386958,"UserName":"富民强企","UseVote":false,"v_isAdminDeleted":false,"v_isAppend":false,"v_isEditOwnDoc":false,"v_lDocModifiedPageNo":0,"v_lDocNo":7,"v_lPageCount":1.00000000000000000e+000,"v_lUserID":0,"v_lUserLevel":100,"v_SeeUserId":0},"isfirstfloor":false},{"docinfo":{},"foolrinfo":{"del_w":false,"DelTime":"","Emote":0,"fd_1_sel_product":false,"fd_id":0,"floorcontent":"<div class=doc_txt  id=\"text_9_0\"><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><span style=\"font-family:黑体;\">第九章<span><span>&nbsp;\r\n<\/span><\/span>信息披露<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span>&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第一百六十条<span><span> <\/span><\/span><\/span><\/b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行应当通过公开渠道，向投资者和社会公众披露相关信息，确保信息披露的集中性、可访问性和公开性。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第一百六十一条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">资本充足率的信息披露应至少包括以下内容：<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（一）风险管理体系：信用风险、市场风险、操作风险、流动性风险及其它重要风险的管理目标、政策、流程以及组织架构和相关部门的职能。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（二）资本充足率计算范围。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（三）资本数量、构成及各级资本充足率。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（四）信用风险、市场风险、操作风险的计量方法，风险计量体系的重大变更，以及相应的资本要求变化。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（五）信用风险、市场风险、操作风险及其它重要风险暴露和评估的定性和定量信息。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（六）内部资本充足评估方法以及影响资本充足率的其它相关因素。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（七）薪酬的定性信息和相关定量信息。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行应当按照本办法附件<span>15<\/span>的要求充分披露资本充足<span>率相关<\/span>信息。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第一百六十二条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行应当保证披露信息的真实性、准确性和完整性。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第一百六十三条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">本办法规定的披露内容是资本充足<span>率信息<\/span>披露的最低要求，商业银行应当遵循充分披露的原则，并根据监管政策变化及时调整披露事项。<span>\r\n<\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第一百六十四条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行采用资本计量高级方法的，并行期内应至少披露本办法规定的定性信息和资本底线的定量信息。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第一百六十五条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行可以不披露专有信息或保密信息的具体内容，但应进行一般性披露，并解释原因。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第一百六十六条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行信息披露频率分为临时、季度、半年及年度披露，其中，临时信息应及时披露，季度、半年度信息披露时间为期末后<span>30<\/span>个工作日内，年度信息披露时间为会计年度终了后四个月内。因特殊原因不能按时披露的，应至少提前<span>15<\/span>个工作日向银监会申请延迟披露。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第一百六十七条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行应当分别按照以下频率披露相关信息：<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（一）实收资本或普通股及其<span>它资本<\/span>工具的变化情况应及时披露。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（二）核心一级资本净额、一级资本净额、资本净额、最低资本要求、储备资本和<span>逆周期<\/span>资本要求、附加资本要求、核心一级资本充足率、一级资本充足率以及资本充足率等重要信息应按季披露。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（三）资本充足率计算范围、信用风险暴露总额、逾期及不良贷款总额、贷款损失准备、信用风险资产组合缓释后风险暴露余额、资产证券化风险暴露余额、市场风险资本要求、市场风险期末风险价值及平均风险价值、操作风险情况、股权投资及其损益、银行账户利率风险情况等相关重要信息应每半年披露一次。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第一百六十八条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>\r\n<\/span><\/span><span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">经银监<\/span><\/span><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">会同意，在满足信息披露总体要求的基础上，同时符合以下条件的商业银行可以适当简化信息披露的内容：<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（一）存款规模小于<span>2000<\/span>亿元人民币。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（二）未在境内外上市。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（三）<span>未跨区域<\/span>经营<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">。<\/span><\/p><div align=\"right\"><table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\r\n<tr><td class=\"doc_sign\" align=\"center\"><img data-baiduimageplus-ignore src=\"http://icons.xici.net/u16386958/files/sign.pic\"><\/td><\/tr>\r\n<tr><td class=\"doc_sign\" align=\"center\">\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\"><tr><td class=\"doc_sign\">我的名片：<br>\r\n创建紫金家园，打造职场互动沟通平台；<br>\r\n关注基层民声，创造健康和谐企业氛围；<br>\r\n南京拍客（摄影）：我是南京人，传播真善美！&nbsp;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n本版腾讯微博：http://t.qq.com/zijibank<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;新浪微博：http://weibo.com/jszjrcbank<br>\r\n<\/td><\/tr><\/table>\r\n<\/td><\/tr>\r\n<tr><td class=\"doc_sign\" align=\"center\"><a href=\"http://b1123492.xici.net\" target=\"_blank\">紫金家园<\/a><\/td><\/tr>\r\n<\/table><\/div><\/div>\r\n","isAdminFlag":false,"isCanUpdate":false,"isDel":0,"isHide":0,"isShow":true,"keyThis":"","lDocModifiedCount":1,"LongDate":"12-07-01 22:41","online":false,"really_updated_at":"2012-07-01 22:41:46","ShortDate":"07-01 22:41","ShortDate_i":[],"Url":"/d172277779.u16386958.htm","UserID":16386958,"UserName":"富民强企","UseVote":false,"v_isAdminDeleted":false,"v_isAppend":false,"v_isEditOwnDoc":false,"v_lDocModifiedPageNo":0,"v_lDocNo":8,"v_lPageCount":1.00000000000000000e+000,"v_lUserID":0,"v_lUserLevel":100,"v_SeeUserId":0},"isfirstfloor":false},{"docinfo":{},"foolrinfo":{"del_w":false,"DelTime":"","Emote":0,"fd_1_sel_product":false,"fd_id":0,"floorcontent":"<div class=doc_txt  id=\"text_10_0\"><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><span style=\"font-family:黑体;\">第十章<span><span>&nbsp;\r\n<\/span><\/span>附则<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span>&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第一百六十九条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">农村合作银行、村镇银行、农村信用合作社、农村资金互助社、贷款公司、企业集团财务公司、消费金融公司、金融租赁公司、汽车金融公司参照本办法执行。外国银行在华分行参照本办法规定的风险权重计量人民币风险加权资产。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第一百七十条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">本办法所称的资本计量高级方法包括信用风险内部评级法、市场风险内部模型法和操作风险高级计量法。商业银行采用资本计量高级方法，应当按照本办法附件<span>16<\/span>的规定建立资本计量高级方法验证体系。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第一百七十一条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">银监会对获准采用资本计量高级方法的商业银行设立并行期，并行期自获准采用资本计量高级方法当年底开始，至少持续三年。并行期内，商业银行应按照本办法规定的资本计量高级方法和其它方法并行计量资本充足率，并遵守本办法附件<span>14<\/span>规定的资本底线要求。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">并行期第一年、第二年和第三年的资本底线调整系数分别为<span>95%<\/span>、<span>90%<\/span>和<span>80%<\/span>。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">并行期内，商业银行<span>实际计提<\/span>的贷款损失准备超过预期损失的，低于<span>150%<\/span>拨备覆盖率的超额贷款损失准备计入二级资本的数量不得超过信用风险加权资产的<span>0.6%<\/span>；高于<span>150%<\/span>拨备覆盖率的超额贷款损失准备可全部计入二级资本。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第一百七十二条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行应在<span>2018<\/span>年底前达到本办法规定的资本充足率监管要求，鼓励有条件的商业银行提前达标。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第一百七十三条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">达标过渡期内，商业银行应当制定并实施切实可行的资本充足率分步达标规划，<span>并报银监<\/span>会批准。银监会根据商业银行资本充足率达标规划实施情况，采取相应的监管措施。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第一百七十四条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">达标过渡期内，商业银行应当同时按照《商业银行资本充足率管理办法》和本办法计量并披露并表和非并<span>表资本<\/span>充足率。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第一百七十五条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">达标过渡期内，商业银行可以简化信息披露内容，但应当至少披露资本充足率计算范围、各级资本及扣减项、资本充足率水平、信用风险加权资产、市场风险加权资产、操作风险加权资产和薪酬的重要信息，以及享受过渡期优惠政策的资本工具和监管调整项目。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第一百七十六条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">商业银行计算并<span>表资本<\/span>充足率，因新旧计量规则差异导致少数股东资本可计入资本的数量下降，减少部分从本办法施行之日起分五年逐步实施，即第一年加回<span>80%<\/span>，第二年加回<span>60%<\/span>，第三年加回<span>40%<\/span>，第四年加回<span>20%<\/span>，第五年不再加回。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第一百七十七条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">本办法中采用标准普尔的评级符号，但对商业银行选用外部信用评级公司不做规定；商业银行使用外部评级公司的评级结果应符合本办法附件<span>17<\/span>的规定，并保持连续性。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第一百七十八条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">附件<span>1<\/span>、附件<span>2<\/span>、附件<span>3<\/span>、附件<span>4<\/span>、附件<span>5<\/span>、附件<span>6<\/span>、附件<span>7<\/span>、附件<span>8<\/span>、附件<span>9<\/span>、附件<span>10<\/span>、附件<span>11<\/span>、附件<span>12<\/span>、附件<span>13<\/span>、附件<span>14<\/span>、附件<span>15<\/span>、附件<span>16<\/span>、附件<span>17<\/span>是本办法的组成部分。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（一）<span><span> <\/span><\/span>附件<span>1<\/span>：资本工具合格标准。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（二）<span><span> <\/span><\/span>附件<span>2<\/span>：信用风险权重法表内资产风险权重、表外项目信用转换系数及合格信用风险缓释工具。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（三）<span><span> <\/span><\/span>附件<span>3<\/span>：信用风险内部评级<span>法风险<\/span>加权资产计量规则。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（四）<span><span> <\/span><\/span>附件<span>4<\/span>：信用风险内部评级<span>法风险<\/span>暴露分类标准。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（五）<span><span> <\/span><\/span>附件<span>5<\/span>：信用风险内部评级体系监管要求。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（六）<span><span> <\/span><\/span>附件<span>6<\/span>：信用风险内部评级<span>法风险<\/span>缓释监管要求。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（七）<span><span> <\/span><\/span>附件<span>7<\/span>：专业贷款风险加权资产计量规则。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（八）<span><span> <\/span><\/span>附件<span>8<\/span>：交易对手信用风险加权资产计量规则。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（九）<span><span> <\/span><\/span>附件<span>9<\/span>：资产证券化风险加权资产计量规则。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（十）<span><span> <\/span><\/span>附件<span>10<\/span>：市场风险标准法计量规则。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（十一）<span><span>&nbsp; <\/span><\/span>附件<span>11<\/span>：市场风险内部模型法监管要求。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（十二）<span><span>&nbsp; <\/span><\/span>附件<span>12<\/span>：操作风险资本计量监管要求。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（十三）<span><span>&nbsp; <\/span><\/span>附件<span>13<\/span>：商业银行风险评估标准。<span>\r\n<\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（十四）<span><span>&nbsp; <\/span><\/span>附件<span>14<\/span>：资本计量高级方法监督检查。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（十五）<span><span>&nbsp; <\/span><\/span>附件<span>15<\/span>：信息披露要求。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（十六）<span><span>&nbsp; <\/span><\/span>附件<span>16<\/span>：资本计量高级方法验证要求。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30pt;\"><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">（十七）<span><span>&nbsp; <\/span><\/span>附件<span>17<\/span>：外部评级使用规范。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第一百七十九条<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\"><span>\r\n<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">本办法由银监会负责解释。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height:31pt;text-align:left;text-indent:30.1pt;\"><b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">第一百八十条<span><span> <\/span><\/span><\/span><\/b><span\r\nstyle=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">本办法自<span>2013<\/span>年<span>1<\/span>月<span>1<\/span>日起施行。《商业银行资本充足率管理办法》（中国银行业监督管理委员会<span>2004<\/span>年第<span>2<\/span>号令颁布实施，根据<span>2006<\/span>年<span>12<\/span>月<span>28<\/span>日中国银行业监督管理委员会第五十五次主席会议《关于修改<span>&lt;<\/span>商业银行资本充足率管理办法<span>&gt;<\/span>的决定》修正），《商业银行银行账户信用风险暴露分类指引》、《商业银行信用风险内部评级体系监管指引》、《商业银行专业贷款监管资本计量指引》、《商业银行信用风险缓释监管资本计量指引》、《商业银行操作风险监管资本计量指引》（银监发<span>[2008]69<\/span>号），《商业银行资本充足率信息披露指引》（银监发<span>[2009]97<\/span>号），《商业银行资本计量高级方法验证指引》（银监发<span>[2009]104<\/span>号），《商业银行资本充足率监督检查指引》（银监发<span>[2009]109<\/span>号），《商业银行资产证券化风险暴露监管资本计量指引》（银监发<span>[2009]<\/span>）<span>116<\/span>号），\r\n《商业银行市场风险资本计量内部模型法监管指引》（银监发<span>[2010]13<\/span>号），《商业银行资本计量高级方法实施申请和审批指引》（银监发<span>[2010]114<\/span>号）同时废止。本办法施行前出台的有关规章及规范性文件如与本办法不一致的，按照本办法执行。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span>&nbsp;<\/span><\/p><div align=\"right\"><table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\r\n<tr><td class=\"doc_sign\" align=\"center\"><img data-baiduimageplus-ignore src=\"http://icons.xici.net/u16386958/files/sign.pic\"><\/td><\/tr>\r\n<tr><td class=\"doc_sign\" align=\"center\">\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\"><tr><td class=\"doc_sign\">我的名片：<br>\r\n创建紫金家园，打造职场互动沟通平台；<br>\r\n关注基层民声，创造健康和谐企业氛围；<br>\r\n南京拍客（摄影）：我是南京人，传播真善美！&nbsp;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n本版腾讯微博：http://t.qq.com/zijibank<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;新浪微博：http://weibo.com/jszjrcbank<br>\r\n<\/td><\/tr><\/table>\r\n<\/td><\/tr>\r\n<tr><td class=\"doc_sign\" align=\"center\"><a href=\"http://b1123492.xici.net\" target=\"_blank\">紫金家园<\/a><\/td><\/tr>\r\